{"tid":997422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK：共產黨的「三中商」書店","createTime":"2019-01-27T07:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:10:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6d023162a67f25e505a91259bbc16d06a5f0ed","tid":997422,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M6KqCvKTukw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM6KqCvKTukw&d=LfVst80bDa3Z%2FR5Vf3xtfozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e89a5e4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M6KqCvKTukw</a>"},{"pid":"8c42518f4256e5ac0d73692ed4b2446e3f514890","tid":997422,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"只去二樓書店買書，三商中既子出版社唔會買"},{"pid":"9e6e3aa4d05d7f5ad54ee082f52f461b7d7da9b5","tid":997422,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:10:04.000Z","msg":"中聯辦經營香港超過半數書店（都屬大品牌、各區有旺鋪或地鋪），行內人謂，一般書籍大約有七至八成在三中商書店售出，雖不致於壟斷香港書市，但市場份額極大，影響力強。近年，內地敏感「禁書」已於三中商絕迹，一些批評政府、有關社運傘運的書籍，亦不容易在三中商找到。中聯辦作為一個「聯絡」機構，直接插手書市，應被詰問，要解釋；中聯辦有能力透過市場銷售渠道的優勢，影響訊息流通，這是廣大市民應該關注的事。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-054449187.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-054449187.html&d=LfVst80bDa3Z%2FR5Vf3xtfozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=41e82792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%